&lt;h4 id=&#34;交叉熵损失cross-entropy-loss&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#交叉熵损失cross-entropy-loss&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; 交叉熵损失（Cross-Entropy Loss）&lt;/h4&gt;
