\frac{d\sigma(x)}{dx}=\frac{e^{-x}}{\left(1+e^{-x}\right)^2}=\left(\frac{1+e^{-x}-1}{1+e^{-x}}\right)\left(\frac1{1+e^{-x}}\right)=\left(1-\sigma(x)\right)\sigma(x)
